film-matinee

This project is inspired by Echoes0302/clove-cinema:

  https://github.com/Echoes0302/clove-cinema

clove-cinema offers a lightweight local film server for watching films with
AI chat frontends. film-matinee explores the complementary AI-facing layer:
visual sheets, subtitle sidecars, linear chunk reading, and shared annotations.

The local film server portions include code adapted from Echoes0302/clove-cinema
under the MIT License as stated in that project's README.

Project contributors are listed in README.md.
